<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Shell - Category - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/shell/</link><description>This is my new Hugo FixIt site</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 17:02:51 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/shell/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>syntax error near unexpected token 的问题</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/04/syntax-error-near-unexpected-token-%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2015 15:08:54 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/04/syntax-error-near-unexpected-token-%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/linux/unix/">Linux/Unix</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/shell/">Shell</category><description>&lt;p>如果你在windows里写的shell脚本放到linux系统里运行就可以会提示如下错误&lt;code>syntax error near unexpected token &lt;/code> 这是因为两个平台下面的换行符不一样导致的。所以需要转换下格式，&lt;code>Notepad++&lt;/code>就有这个功能。&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>首先打开Notepad++,让脚本显示所有符号，发现是CR LF
&lt;img loading="lazy" src="http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1489?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e6%8d%a2%e8%a1%8c%e9%83%bd%e6%98%afwindows%e7%9a%84CRLF.jpg" alt="图片描述" srcset="http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1489?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e6%8d%a2%e8%a1%8c%e9%83%bd%e6%98%afwindows%e7%9a%84CRLF.jpg&amp;amp;size=small, http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1489?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e6%8d%a2%e8%a1%8c%e9%83%bd%e6%98%afwindows%e7%9a%84CRLF.jpg&amp;amp;size=medium 1.5x, http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1489?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e6%8d%a2%e8%a1%8c%e9%83%bd%e6%98%afwindows%e7%9a%84CRLF.jpg&amp;amp;size=large 2x" data-title="图片描述" class="suffix-invalid suffix-invalid__small suffix-invalid__large" style="background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>我们需要将windows的格式转为linux格式，做如下操作即可。
编辑-&amp;gt;档案格式转换-&amp;gt;转换为UNIX格式
&lt;img loading="lazy" src="http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1490?filename=cpp%20%e8%bd%ac%e6%8d%a2%e4%b8%baUnix%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f.jpg" alt="图片描述" srcset="http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1490?filename=cpp%20%e8%bd%ac%e6%8d%a2%e4%b8%baUnix%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f.jpg&amp;amp;size=small, http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1490?filename=cpp%20%e8%bd%ac%e6%8d%a2%e4%b8%baUnix%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f.jpg&amp;amp;size=medium 1.5x, http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1490?filename=cpp%20%e8%bd%ac%e6%8d%a2%e4%b8%baUnix%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f.jpg&amp;amp;size=large 2x" data-title="图片描述" class="suffix-invalid suffix-invalid__small suffix-invalid__large" style="background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>转换之后，发现回车换行符就变了。再放入linux就不会报错了。
&lt;img loading="lazy" src="http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1491?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e9%83%bd%e6%98%aflinux%e7%9a%84LF%e4%ba%86.jpg" alt="图片描述" srcset="http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1491?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e9%83%bd%e6%98%aflinux%e7%9a%84LF%e4%ba%86.jpg&amp;amp;size=small, http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1491?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e9%83%bd%e6%98%aflinux%e7%9a%84LF%e4%ba%86.jpg&amp;amp;size=medium 1.5x, http://storage.live.com/items/9A8B8BF501A38A36!1491?filename=%e6%89%80%e6%9c%89%e7%9a%84%e9%83%bd%e6%98%aflinux%e7%9a%84LF%e4%ba%86.jpg&amp;amp;size=large 2x" data-title="图片描述" class="suffix-invalid suffix-invalid__small suffix-invalid__large" style="background: url(/images/loading.min.svg) no-repeat center;" onload="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}this.dataset.lazyloaded='';" onerror="this.title=this.dataset.title;for(const i of ['style', 'data-title','onerror','onload']){this.removeAttribute(i);}"/>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>Linux Shell date命令的用法</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2013/03/linux-shell-date%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2013 18:13:00 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2013/03/linux-shell-date%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/linux/unix/">Linux/Unix</category><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/shell/">Shell</category><description>&lt;p>在linux shell编程中，经常用到日期的加减运算，以前都是自己通过expr函数计算，很麻烦。
其实date命令本身提供了日期的加减运算，非常方便。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>例如：得到昨天的时间&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">date +%Y%m%d –date&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>”-1 day”&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>date的用法:&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>